Narrative:
Shahid Kapoor and Ishaan Khatter dance to Michael Jackson Song.
Actors and brothers Shahid Kapoor and Ishaan Khatter are not just good actors but definitely good dancers also. Recently the two danced on Michael Jackson's Smooth Criminal. In their dance video we can also see their mom Neliima Azeem, a Kathak dancer, making a cameo . The two of them dancing  completely in sync to Michael Jackson's song at their home. Sharing the video on Instagram Shahid captioned it, "MJ in PJ!". Ishaan khatter commented to the video, " Jamma jamma pyjamma. " He also again commented on the picture, " Mom in back being the cutest."
